{"tid":2360452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印尼客機墜毀　發現殘骸和一些遇難者遺體","createTime":"2021-01-09T18:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T05:46:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f7211356d8b18b5b7ee7541a3a6b4e44aea43f12","tid":2360452,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T18:25:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569586-20210110.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569586-20210110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=45dac7a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569586-20210110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7e4cb5d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569586-20210110.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n印尼一架國內線客機起飛後不久，墜毀在首都雅加達附近海域，海岸巡邏船已抵達墜機海域，發現客機殘骸和一些遇難者遺體。<br />\n<br />\n出事的是印尼三佛齊航空公司一架波音737-500客機客機，載著62名乘客和機員，周六從雅加達起飛，原定前往西加里曼丹省首府坤甸，但起飛後4分鐘失聯，其後被發現墜毀。航班追蹤網站說，這架客機在不到1分鐘內急降3千米。<br />\n  <br />\n目擊者說，看到和聽到至少一次爆炸。客機墜落海後爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐印尼大使館引述印尼方面表示，經初步核實，機上無外籍乘客。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，這架失事客機1994年5月試飛，加入三佛齊航空機隊8年。"},{"pid":"646b1c8f6d8fde7bc4a0eff7b644c842e8fd6f0e","tid":2360452,"uid":1354,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T18:28:30.000Z","msg":"2021<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44435b0a275c5e2af54e35d87e4f034285fa88ca","tid":2360452,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T18:30:09.000Z","msg":"🖐🏻🦶🏻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ad69de0e9ae5e00b9a7e5bee5ece5b52ac9698","tid":2360452,"uid":367255,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T